@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pinhsq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.cos(0.28) * 0.47)
    v2 = (wp.cos(v2) + v0)
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v2 + 0.64)) - wp.exp((tmp + 0.77 / v1 + 0.27)))
    data[tid] = v0
